{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"9002","heading":"Entrepreneurial development","label":"9002 Entrepreneurial development","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/ch116/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Amendments2020—Subsec. (b)(3)(A). designated existing provisions as cl. (i), inserted heading, and added cl. (ii).Pub. L. 116–260","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective Date of 2020 Amendment, , , provided that:Pub. L. 116–260, div. N, title III, § 346(b)134 Stat. 2052Dec. 27, 2020“The amendments made by subsection (a) [amending this section] shall be effective as if included in the CARES Act (; ).”Public Law 116–136134 Stat. 281"],"amendments":["Amendments2020—Subsec. (b)(3)(A). designated existing provisions as cl. (i), inserted heading, and added cl. (ii).Pub. L. 116–260","Effective Date of 2020 Amendment, , , provided that:Pub. L. 116–260, div. N, title III, § 346(b)134 Stat. 2052Dec. 27, 2020“The amendments made by subsection (a) [amending this section] shall be effective as if included in the CARES Act (; ).”Public Law 116–136134 Stat. 281"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Definitions","label":"a Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F1%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"quantity and lead time, including the number of shipments of components and delays in shipments;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F1%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"quality, including shortages in supply for quality control reasons; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/A/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F1%2FA%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"technology, including a compromised payment network;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"staffing challenges;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F1%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a decrease in gross receipts or customers; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F1%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a closure;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a small business development center; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a women’s business center;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the term “small business development center” has the meaning given the term in ; andsection 632 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the term “women’s business center” means a women’s business center described in .section 656 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Education, training, and advising grants","label":"b Education, training, and advising grants","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Administration may provide financial assistance in the form of grants to resource partners to provide education, training, and advising to covered small business concerns.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Use of funds","label":"2 Use of funds","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"accessing and applying for resources provided by the Administration and other Federal resources relating to access to capital and business resiliency;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the hazards and prevention of the transmission and communication of COVID–19 and other communicable diseases;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the potential effects of COVID–19 on the supply chains, distribution, and sale of products of covered small business concerns and the mitigation of those effects;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F2%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the management and practice of telework to reduce possible transmission of COVID–19;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"E","heading":null,"label":"E","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2/E","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F2%2FE","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the management and practice of remote customer service by electronic or other means;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"F","heading":null,"label":"F","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2/F","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F2%2FF","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the risks of and mitigation of cyber threats in remote customer service or telework practices;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"G","heading":null,"label":"G","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2/G","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F2%2FG","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the mitigation of the effects of reduced travel or outside activities on covered small business concerns during COVID–19 or similar occurrences; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"H","heading":null,"label":"H","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2/H","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F2%2FH","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any other relevant business practices necessary to mitigate the economic effects of COVID–19 or similar occurrences.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Grant determination","label":"3 Grant determination","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"Small business development centers","label":"A Small business development centers","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":"In general","label":"i In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F3%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Administration shall award 80 percent of funds authorized to carry out this subsection to small business development centers, which shall be awarded pursuant to a formula jointly developed, negotiated, and agreed upon, with full participation of both parties, between the association formed under and the Administration.section 648(a)(3)(A) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":"Clarification of use","label":"ii Clarification of use","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F3%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Awards made under clause (i) shall be in addition to, and separate from, any amounts appropriated to make grants under and such an award may be used to complement and support such a grant, except that priority with respect to the receipt of that assistance shall be given to small business development centers that have been affected by issues described in paragraph (2).section 648(a) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Women’s business centers","label":"B Women’s business centers","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Administration shall award 20 percent of funds authorized to carry out this subsection to women’s business centers, which shall be awarded pursuant to a process established by the Administration in consultation with recipients of assistance.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":"No matching funds required","label":"C No matching funds required","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F3%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Matching funds shall not be required for any grant under this subsection.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Goals and metrics","label":"4 Goals and metrics","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F4%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"take into consideration the extent of the circumstances relating to the spread of COVID–19, or similar occurrences, that affect covered small business concerns located in the areas covered by the resource partner, particularly in rural areas or economically distressed areas;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F4%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"generally follow the use of funds outlined in paragraph (2), but shall not restrict the activities of resource partners in responding to unique situations; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4/A/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F4%2FA%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"encourage resource partners to develop and provide services to covered small business concerns.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Public availability","label":"B Public availability","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/b/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fb%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Administrator shall make publicly available the methodology by which the Administrator and resource partners jointly develop the metrics and goals described in subparagraph (A).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Resource partner association grants","label":"c Resource partner association grants","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/c/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fc%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"1 online platform that consolidates resources and information available across multiple Federal agencies for small business concerns related to COVID–19; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/c/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fc%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a training program to educate resource partner counselors, members of the Service Corps of Retired Executives established under , and counselors at veterans business outreach centers described in on the resources and information described in subparagraph (A).section 637(b)(1)(B) of this titlesection 657b of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Goals and metrics","label":"2 Goals and metrics","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Goals and metrics for the funds made available under this subsection shall be jointly developed, negotiated, and agreed upon, with full participation of both parties, between the association or associations receiving a grant under this subsection and the Administrator.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Report","label":"d Report","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fd%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the programs and services developed and provided by the Administration and resource partners under subsection (b);","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fd%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the initial efforts to provide those services under subsection (b); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/1/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fd%2F1%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the online platform and training developed and provided by the Administration and the association or associations under subsection (c); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9002/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9002%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendmen